UndeadLoot Revived
==================

This is a community rework of "UndeadLoot" by 7ModsToDead, updated for 7 Days to Die V3.0.

Original mod, concept, and loot tables:
    7ModsToDead  -  https://www.patreon.com/7modstodead

The original mod was published under these terms:
    "This mod is free to use and modify, but please credit the author and provide a
     link to the original source."

This rework is distributed under those same terms. You may use, modify, and redistribute
it provided that you:
  - credit 7ModsToDead as the original author and link to the original mod, and
  - credit this rework (iotshelnik) and link back to this repository.

V3.0 rework (code and mechanics): iotshelnik

Bundled third-party component:
  - 0Harmony.dll (Harmony by Andreas Pardeike) - MIT License - https://github.com/pardeike/Harmony
